:353182,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf222beee47b9e8324a3671db0e50e750b119679","tid":353182,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:36:06.000Z","msg":"得罪印度，一帶一路功能廢一半，對人口老化嚴重既中國帶來嚴重經濟打擊，之前所有戰略部署都付諸流水，仲有，中國既能源線係經過印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔理印度霸地，就俾中國內既國家主義者視為紙老虎，失去人民支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d66fe05febc28322ca3d0848ba7ab1d9c830c04","tid":353182,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">再拖落去，習總既強人印象就會失去</span><br />\n今次又無得用經濟制裁，反而印度可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩年前, 緬甸戰機 係雲南自出自入, 炸死五個中國人<br />\n<br />\n習總既形象已經玩完啦"},{"pid":"649cbafa0000b02a60db626e8bf0e25f285a9a5f","tid":353182,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:59:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">再拖落去，習總既強人印象就會失去</span><br />\n今次又無得用經濟制裁，反而印度可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩年前, 緬甸戰機 係雲南自出自入, 炸死五個中國人<br />\n習總既形象已經玩完啦</blockquote><br />\n傻啦，邊有中國人記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade2ce8db078a2996a2b93f9610410c21c2dc8d3","tid":353182,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eee90e4f83d8f095a2161213a5ae7bd989b4b96","tid":353182,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">再拖落去，習總既強人印象就會失去</span><br />\n今次又無得用經濟制裁，反而印度可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩年前, 緬